short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Share on various social media sites

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Simple and easy to share web pages on social medias, including wechat, weibo, twitter, facebook, douban, reddit, etc.
Want to share in more websites? don't hesitate to tell me on github: 

https://github.com/revir/need-more-share2
 
It's open-source, derived from a pure Javascript library of sharing, which can be used on blog platforms or any website you have. Visit github to find out.
